Class SetPairBulkTraverser<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type

    public class SetPairBulkTraverser<K>
extends SetPairTraverser<K>
    Extracts Embeddings iteratively from a given graph by traversing the graph according to a given TraversalCode. For the iteration the traverser uses Flink bulk iteration.
